Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.98,0:00:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}但是 還沒完 吾輩的力量可不止這點程度
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.74,0:00:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}別忘了還有我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.58,0:00:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}華麗綻放吧 吞龍咬焰花
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.42,0:00:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}天霧辰明流劍術中傳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.26,0:00:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}陸屑蜂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.22,0:00:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}還沒完啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.74,0:02:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這種數值上升率太不正常了 應該立刻停止
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.54,0:02:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}極限控制權已經由莉姆希轉交給他了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.86,0:02:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}現在已經沒有辦法了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.93,0:02:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不是還可以強制停止嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.57,0:02:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}雖然可能會對擬形體的中樞造成損害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.74,0:02:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}但如果有必要 就應該這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.38,0:02:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}因為責任在你身上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.78,0:02:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}責任啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.66,0:03:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我啊 就算在這種情況下 依舊相信他們兩個哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.42,0:03:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}綾斗 那究竟是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.97,0:03:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我應該再早點發現的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.42,0:03:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}說起來 不論多麼堅固的防禦屏障
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.54,0:03:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}都不可能正面抵擋住黑爐魔劍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.85,0:03:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}之前能夠做到這一點的就只有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.98,0:03:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}霸潰血鐮嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.42,0:03:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}沒錯 除非是同等級的純星煌式武裝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.78,0:03:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不然是不可能抵擋住黑爐魔劍的攻擊的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.57,0:03:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}恐怕阿爾迪使用了萬應精晶作為動力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.70,0:03:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}等等 這麼說現在的阿爾迪...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.01,0:03:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}失控了!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.66,0:03:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不 他確實是沒法完全掌控那股力量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.50,0:03:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}但我估計阿爾迪他...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.46,0:03:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.90,0:04:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這...這才是吾輩真正的力量嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.22,0:04:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}難怪主人會如此謹慎對待
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.82,0:04:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}他控制住了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.74,0:04:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}好了 雖然萬分不捨 不過差不多該決出勝負了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.78,0:04:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}吾輩來也
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.94,0:04:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}綾斗 快退後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.50,0:04:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}綻放吧 大輪爆耀華
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.86,0:04:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.06,0:04:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那麼 吾輩也還你一招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.14,0:04:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.10,0:04:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}好了 爆炸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.27,0:05:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}來來 繼續啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}綾斗 你沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.19,0:05:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}尤莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.59,0:05:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我...我沒事...雖然很想這麼說 但實在是有些不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.03,0:05:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}至少要是我的速度能比他更快 那就能分出勝負了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.35,0:05:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}速度嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.75,0:05:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}等...等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.63,0:05:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}尤莉絲 你要做什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.67,0:06:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我記得以前聽克勞蒂雅說過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.79,0:06:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}原本黑爐魔劍會化為對使用者而言最順手的形狀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.59,0:06:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}如果能做到這一點 應該就有勝算了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.87,0:06:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}星辰力的細微調整不是我的強項
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.51,0:06:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}應該說 非常不擅長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.19,0:06:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那這個就讓我來負責吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.07,0:06:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你只要對它注入星辰力就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.10,0:06:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}知...知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.95,0:06:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}綾斗 想像一下 你用起來最順手的形狀大小
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.71,0:06:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}最理想的黑爐魔劍的造型
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.71,0:07:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}完成了 這是屬於你...天霧綾斗的黑爐魔劍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.43,0:07:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這就是我理想中的形狀...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.75,0:07:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這場比賽 我能做的就是這些了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.27,0:07:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}尤莉絲?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.67,0:07:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}之後就交給你了 綾斗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.99,0:07:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}明白了 尤莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.55,0:07:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}抱歉 等很久了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.71,0:07:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不會 吾輩剛才也出了些問題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.19,0:08:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}靠這一擊決出勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.23,0:08:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}得手了
