Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.87,0:12:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}黑貓機關金眼七號 我記得名字是叫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.99,0:12:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}威爾納對吧?
