Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.23,0:12:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你究竟...是聽誰的命令在行動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.31,0:12:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你猜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.91,0:12:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}恭喜你奪冠 不愧是我的綾斗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.99,0:12:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}謝謝你 紗夜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.87,0:13:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}真是非常精彩的戰鬥 不愧是我的綾斗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.87,0:13:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這多虧了紗夜她們 真的非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.15,0:13:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不 不只是我們的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.03,0:13:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}還有綺凜和夜吹 馬克菲爾也有幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.07,0:13:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}雷士達嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.70,0:13:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你...你用不著和我道謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.30,0:13:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}是夜吹那傢伙脅迫我 我不得已才來幫忙的罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.67,0:13:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}謝謝你 雷士達 幫了我大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.51,0:13:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}咦 說起來夜吹人呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.39,0:13:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那傢伙半途就開溜了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.18,0:13:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}叫別人出來幫忙 自己卻腳底抹油
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.35,0:13:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}下次再見到他 我絕對饒不了他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.47,0:13:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這是替身術啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.87,0:13:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}慘了 這件好像是新衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.43,0:14:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不過 很抱歉 綾斗 最後沒能抓住犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.99,0:14:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}用不著道歉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.10,0:14:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}總之大家都平安無事 這就是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.38,0:14:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}綾斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.55,0:14:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}老子要回去了 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.27,0:14:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}對了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.23,0:14:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}怎麼了 雷士達
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.39,0:14:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}嘛 那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.79,0:14:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}姑且還是祝賀你一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.83,0:14:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}雷士達?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.19,0:14:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}馬克菲爾君也真是一點都不坦率呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.71,0:14:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那個 請問...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.07,0:14:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你有什麼事?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.51,0:14:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}沙沙宮紗夜 我希望與你再戰一場
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.99,0:15:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我不明白這麼做的理由 我們已經輸給你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.59,0:15:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}在昨天的半決賽中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.75,0:15:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你和沙沙宮博士的煌式武裝明顯凌駕於莉姆希之上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.27,0:15:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}但是 我沒能贏過合體之後的阿爾迪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.11,0:15:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}合體狀態的阿爾迪相當於是使用了純星煌式武裝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.15,0:15:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}而我們獅子派的理念
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.31,0:15:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}是與純星煌式武裝這種不穩定的武器相對立的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.51,0:15:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}因此 我個人並不認為那是一場勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.03,0:15:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我知道了 那就再戰一場分個高下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.55,0:15:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}下次我一定會把你轟得體無完膚 徹底贏得勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.95,0:15:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那我們就更上一層樓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.31,0:15:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.03,0:16:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我想聽聽你關於前幾天的那件事的答覆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.34,0:16:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}答覆?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.83,0:16:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}就是要不要和我們聯手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.95,0:16:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.39,0:16:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}答覆當然是... No
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.95,0:16:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我果然還是對你們不太感興趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.75,0:16:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不過 你那第三台擬形體 真的有辦法完成嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.99,0:16:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你不是找不到合適的萬應精晶嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.51,0:16:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}原來如此 真是了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.11,0:16:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}關於她的事情 我甚至都沒告訴過卡蜜拉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.19,0:16:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}應該說真不愧是雷渥夫嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.50,0:16:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我知道了 如果只是聽你說說 也未嘗不可
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.63,0:16:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}行 我會再聯絡你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.11,0:16:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}好了 不知道接下來會出現什麼妖魔鬼怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.55,0:17:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}恭喜你獲得冠軍 綾斗前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.39,0:17:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.59,0:17:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不過我們能贏也是全靠綺凜你們的努力呀
